Class Pair

  • java.lang.Object
    • Pair

  • public class Pair
extends java.lang.Object
    Pair is the class that encapsulates a Student object and a Teacher object. This pairing includes the score (assigned by ScoringEngine), the mutual times at which both individuals can attend a lesson, and the instrument for which the lesson will be administered.
